included.description:

included.description:
Client: Closet Collective-  Closet Collective is a company that provides a platform for  women to lend and borrow one another's high end clothing and accessories. Closet Collective tasked us with providing clarity and suggestions for  website redesign in order to increase new user signups and conversions for monthly subscriptions.

-Conducted contextual inquiry to reveal tacit knowledge 

-Developed personas through research to define Closet Collective's userbase

-Coordinated and conducted diary study with 3 participants to find pain points and streamline the rental box process

-Extensively studied user on-boarding process so it could be simplified and streamlined

-Developed storyboards, user stories and user flows to show how our personas would interact with the product

-Conducted A/B User testing with wireframes and copy to ensure clarity and usability within our prototypes

-Created deliverables including high fidelity interactive prototypes made with Axure and Sketch
